title: Ambassador's Monthly Task List
body:
Vote to Enact the Ambassador Monthly Task list and related minimum reported completions therein. This list can be changed with a unanimous Ambassador agreement. "This form will serve as a task checklist for all Ambassadors, whom need to complete at least 3 tasks per month. To mark a task complete, it must be done the listed (req #) of times." 
Full Copy of current Task list here>>
